<center><h1>IMDB Movie Database Analysis</h1></center>

<p></p>
<p>This project pulled data for 1100 Hallmark movies into a SQLite database from a public IMDB dataset of 2M records. The program provided a Web UI and a console menu, various search and report functions, and performed a Jupyter Notebook and network graph analysis to find the "most connected" actors and actresses, and relative "distance"" between them.</p>

